.TH BJCJ "1"

.SH NAME
.B bjcj.pl
- Blockbench Java To Changed Java Model Converter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./bjcj.pl
-n 
.I FILE
-p
.I ANIMATION_PRESET

.SH DESCRIPTION
bjcj.pl is a model converter. It expects a path to a java model file after -n option animation preset after the -p option, and prints the converted class to STDOUT.

